1122
01:36:10,008 --> 01:36:14,875
We go into this profession because of our love for the children and our desire to make a difference in the world.

1123
01:36:15,596 --> 01:36:17,579
And as educators, really,

1124
01:36:23,143 --> 01:36:25,205
As educators, we reap many benefits.

1125
