We develop relationships with students and parents that we carry much further than the current year that we have taught these children.

1126
01:36:32,433 --> 01:36:34,556
We receive emails or letters of thanks.

1127
01:36:35,036 --> 01:36:41,343
We get friend requests from former students or parents, and we get visits from students years after they're gone from our classroom.

1128
01:36:41,864 --> 01:36:44,266
