1145
01:38:03,062 --> 01:38:07,184
We have research and we are supplementing and finding materials on our own time.

1146
01:38:08,124 --> 01:38:16,074
Elementary educators have had to adjust to a new block scheduling that leaves little opportunity to target instruction and differentiate for our students.

1147
01:38:16,794 --> 01:38:23,682
