1171
01:40:42,917 --> 01:40:43,537
And you know what?

1172
01:40:43,777 --> 01:40:45,458
It is all about the children.

1173
01:40:45,878 --> 01:40:46,979
That's why we're all here.

1174
01:40:47,499 --> 01:40:51,360
That's why we stepped up to the plate and went above and beyond what was asked of us.

1175
01:40:51,780 --> 01:40:59,742
