02:00:18,092 --> 02:00:25,873
a legislative budget to be used by the council to hire a consultant or attorney to help you finalize the comp plan and housing production plan.

1349
02:00:28,294 --> 02:00:33,175
We have also been working with our team at the schools over the last week and we have heard them.

1350
02:00:33,295 --> 02:00:39,996
We are allocating an additional 300,000 in ARPA monies for essential positions that need to be restored tomorrow.

1351
02:00:41,336 --> 02:00:43,437
I called you all today to recap your priorities.

1352
02:00:43,717 --> 02:00:45,857
Thank you to those who text me back or call me back

1353
02:00:46,145 --> 02:00:50,688
I've heard you over the last three weeks and today, which is why we've made these adjustments.

1354
02:00:51,249 --> 02:00:59,575
It does not cover all of your or my priorities, but I feel I've met the needs that matter to us most to be able to get a better budget approved tonight.

1355
02:01:00,296 --> 02:01:09,883
Thank you for your consideration and for allowing me to present my seven page proposed, my seven page speech this evening, I'm able to take

1356
02:01:10,243 --> 02:01:19,849
questions now before I hand it over to our full financial team, our department heads, I know we have CLA on the call as well for any questions you may have.

1357
02:01:21,109 --> 02:01:21,810
Thank you, Madam Mayor.

1358
02:01:22,850 --> 02:01:24,231
Thank you, Madam President.

1359
02:01:24,271 --> 02:01:25,672
Thank you, Madam Mayor for your presentation.

1360
02:01:25,712 --> 02:01:26,392
It's good to see you.

1361
02:01:27,073 --> 02:01:27,333
You too.

1362
02:01:28,400 --> 02:01:39,350
The first thing I just want to say is, you know, certainly I was one to vote for an increase in the CFO salary, but I will say, we've been waiting six months for legal opinion to go to third reading on that.

1363
02:01:39,470 --> 02:01:41,132
