1419
02:08:13,019 --> 02:08:14,920
I don't think that the citizens of Medford

1420
02:08:15,580 --> 02:08:24,946
can afford another year of level funded budgets, which mean effective service cuts, which means we're having people constantly going around and saying, why can't we do this?

1421
02:08:25,006 --> 02:08:25,767
Why can't we do that?

1422
02:08:25,887 --> 02:08:27,528
